<item>
            <title>[CAMEL-16296] camel-as2 - Restarting bundle on karaf causes PortNumberInUse error</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CAMEL-16296</link>
                <project id="12311211" key="CAMEL">Camel</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;I try to create as2 server using camel-as2. I created a simple server in camel-context and installed bundle on Karaf.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;image-wrap&quot; style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/attachment/13021513/13021513_image-2021-03-03-13-48-10-854.png&quot; style=&quot;border: 0px solid black&quot; /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;When I install bundle in Karaf for the first time, everything is fine. When I uninstall and install bundle in Karaf I get an error.&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;image-wrap&quot; style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/attachment/13021512/13021512_image-2021-03-03-13-50-11-683.png&quot; style=&quot;border: 0px solid black&quot; /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
